attributes.title: disappointed and dissatisfied.
attributes.review:
i see an abundance of these 5 star reviews belong to my fellow Trump supporters, to which i have to say 
1. MAGA!! 4 more years! 
but, regretfully,
2. i don’t believe you guys are being completely honest within your words. yes, Trump is one of the greatest people to ever live, and we are so lucky to have him leading this country, but this app is distasteful to the fascist movement! 
there were multiple problems with this application. 

here are a couple things i think that could make this app more appealing, authentic, and enjoyable:
- pictures of Robert Kennedy, who is way hotter than Trump (which, as most of my fellow MAGA bros are thinking, is QUITE the statement... cause HUBBA HUBBA!!) 
- more representation of his supporters of his supporters. how am i supposed to become aroused without any pictures of my MAGA boys? i want to see more nike golf shirts, more cowboy boots, and more crooked teeth, goddamnit!! 
- less red, white and blue. it hurts my eyes.
